## R Startup Configuration
## Create .Rprofile in your project directory:

# In R:
# Ensure project R library is first in path
.libPaths(c("/project/R_libs", .libPaths()))

# Set working directory to project
if (interactive()) {
    setwd("/project")
    cat("Working directory set to /project\n")
    cat("Available libraries:\n")
    print(.libPaths())
}

